    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Berserker sphere, Shatter Earth.</p>\n<p>You may choose to break the ground as you move. Whenever you leave a square, you may choose to make that square difficult terrain. Your base attack bonus must be greater than the hardness of the surface to use this ability. This difficult terrain remains until it is cleared as a standard action (clearing 1 square within the creature&#8217;s reach, provoking an attack of opportunity) or repaired with a spell or effect such as the mending spell or the repair ability of the Creation sphere.</p>\n",
